            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "\u00a9 2021, The Author(s), under exclusive licence to Springer Nature America, Inc.We introduce the TRUST4 open-source algorithm for reconstruction of immune receptor repertoires in \u03b1\u03b2/\u03b3\u03b4 T cells and B cells from RNA-sequencing (RNA-seq) data. Compared with competing methods, TRUST4 supports both FASTQ and BAM format and is faster and more sensitive in assembling longer\u2014even full-length\u2014receptor repertoires. TRUST4 can also call repertoire sequences from single-cell RNA-seq (scRNA-seq) data without V(D)J enrichment, and is compatible with both SMART-seq and 5\u2032 10x Genomics platforms.",
